	{ type = 'two_column', left_title = 'Propose a talk', left_body = "Send a short abstract that explains your question, method, and the discussion you want to have with the audience. Include your preferred format and any accessibility needs.\n\n**Important dates (TBA)**\n\n- Call for submissions opens: TBA\n- Submission deadline: TBA\n- Notifications: TBA", right_title = 'Archival submission', right_body = "**Call for archival submissions**\n\nWe welcome research talks, work-in-progress ideas, and practice-facing case studies.\n\n**Submissions & review (OpenReview)**\n\nSubmissions and reviews are managed in OpenReview.\n\n**Proceedings (CEUR-WS)**\n\nAccepted papers are planned for an open-access CEUR-WS proceedings volume (CC BY 4.0).\n\n**Important dates (TBA)**\n\n- Call for submissions opens: TBA\n- Submission deadline: TBA\n- Notifications: TBA\n- Camera-ready: TBA" },
